      "id": "https://uofa.net/synth/validation/nagaraja-f1717-stiffness-comparison",
      "type": "ValidationResult",
      "name": "FEA vs experimental stiffness comparison — ASTM F1717 compression-bending, N=11"
    },
    {
      "id": "https://uofa.net/synth/validation/nagaraja-f1717-yield-load-comparison",
